name: A lot of... Strange Enemies!
description:
You are a cute pink character looking to reach the misterious PINK PORTAL to leave the dungeon.

Unfortunately, a lot of nests from different enemies spawned in the dungeon. Discover and destroy them to be able to escape the dungeon.

CONTROLS:

AWSD - Moves the player horizontally

SPACE - Jump

MOUSE LEFT CLICK - Shoot

Tips: 

1 - Yes, you can swin in the water. :)

DISCLAIMER:

Tileset made by https://v3x3d.itch.io/retro-lines
